# Tag API Endpoints

## Create a new tag

POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tag
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "golang",
  "description": "Articles related to golang and AI applications",
  "tag_icon": "https://example.com/icon.png",
  "tag_image": "https://example.com/image.png"
}

###

## Get all tags

GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tag

###

## Get popular tags

GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tag/popular

###

## Get tag by ID

GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tag/1

###

## Get tag by slug

GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tag/slug/golang

###

## Update a tag (full update)

PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tag/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "langchain",
  "description": "Articles related to langchain and AI applications",
  "tag_icon": "https://example.com/icon.png",
  "tag_image": null
}

###

## Partially update a tag

PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tag/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tag_image": "https://example.com/image.png"
}

###

## Delete a tag

DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tag/8

